                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Sarah L.</strong> - Restaurant Owner, Oregon District
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Living in Oakwood, we needed garage flooring that matched our home's quality. 
                  The team delivered beautiful results and the coating has held up perfectly 
                  through Ohio's weather extremes."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
