              <ul>
                <li>Downtown Dayton and Central Business District</li>
                <li>Kettering and South Dayton suburbs</li>
                <li>Centerville and Washington Township</li>
                <li>Oakwood and historic districts</li>
                <li>Huber Heights and northern communities</li>
                <li>Wright-Patterson AFB area</li>
                <li>University of Dayton vicinity</li>
                <li>Oregon Historic District</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="areas-column">
              <h3>Specialized Expertise Areas</h3>
              <p>
                Our Dayton-specific services include:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Industrial Facilities:</strong> Aerospace and manufacturing flooring</li>
                <li><strong>Commercial Properties:</strong> Retail and office building solutions</li>
                <li><strong>Healthcare Facilities:</strong> Hospital and clinic compliance coatings</li>
                <li><strong>Educational Institutions:</strong> University and school flooring systems</li>
                <li><strong>Historic Properties:</strong> Preservation-appropriate solutions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="contact-content">
            <div class="contact-info">
              <h2>Ready to Start Your Dayton Concrete Project?</h2>
              <p>
                Contact Queen City Surface Coatings today for professional concrete contracting 
