                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Email:</strong> info@queencitysurface.com
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Service Area:</strong> Dayton, OH and all of Montgomery County
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Business Hours:</strong> Monday-Saturday 7AM-7PM
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="service-promise">
                <h3>Our Dayton Service Commitment</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Free estimates with detailed project analysis</li>
                  <li>Industrial and commercial specification compliance</li>
                  <li>Licensed and insured in Ohio</li>
                  <li>Lifetime warranty on workmanship</li>
                  <li>Montgomery County's most experienced team</li>
